Lisa Skinner, 52, shot her estranged husband Bradley Skinner, 59, after he broke into her home in South Huntsville, Alabama, around 6 p.m.
She opened fire with a shotgun, hitting him in the chest, causing life-threatening injuries .
Her mother ran from the house to a nearby house and called 911 .
Police say Mr Skinner was armed with both a pistol and a large knife .
Mr Skinner had been ordered to undergo a psychiatric evaluation before a court hearing next month .